\begin_inset Formula $\widetilde{E}_{g}$
\end_inset

 nontrivially.
 Indeed, let 
\begin_inset Formula $\{e_{\sigma}\}$
\end_inset

 denote the homogeneous basis of 
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

